As far as how many you put on your list you can put as many as your heart desires.  Say if the limit is 250pp as an example.  Someone buys you an item that is worth 100pp, then gets you a couple other things maybe worth 75pp each.  Jus lookin at what the cap is for what a person can get.  <br>
